picoc: aot son-optimizing C89->{RV32I,LLVM} compiler
usage: cargo run compilec89 ./path/to/file.c
disclaimer: this is a one man effort to compile quake. beware of dragons.
references: cooper, siek, muchnick, møller, rastello, click
versions:
- 0.1.1: hackable. quakeable. -O1able.
- 0.1.2: jitable. ldable. -O2able.
